        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p><hr /><p>You call out to an enemy in distress, promising them a future of unending pain. Choose an enemy with the sickened condition that you can see within 120 feet. That creature takes @Damage[max(10,(floor(@actor.level/2)*2))d4[mental]] damage with a @Check[will|against:class-spell|basic] save against your class DC or spell DC, whichever is higher. At 12th level and every 2 levels thereafter, the damage increases by 2d4.</p>"
